      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0423P1_20040629_WH_57'>  </a>
        <blockquote class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <cite class='member author entry-title unmatched-member'></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I conclude by reading something from a note from Rob Johnson, who said:
            <q>I am dismayed that there has been only one upheld complaint against Dialer fraud since February 1 by ICSTIS. I am led to believe that there is underlying 70 per cent. non-collection of levied fines.</q>
            If those companies are based offshore, the situation is difficult, but the whole process seems to be tipping over, and we need quick service to ensure that ICSTIS is brought back in line. In the longer term, we may need a new regime.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
