            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_21wh' title='Col. 21WH &mdash; HC Deb 29 June 2004 vol 423 c21WH' name='column_21wh' href='#column_21wh' rel='bookmark'>21WH</a>
            Act 1990 might result in extradition. However, until we get worldwide agreement that all nations must cooperate, there will be mayhem on the internet, just as there could have been mayhem on broadcast frequencies.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
